Crazy Srbin Production

01:57:11.604 --> 01:57:14.871
Prav, dajmo.
Še enkrat.

01:57:17.454 --> 01:57:21.246
Tišina, prosim.
Bodite tiho.

01:57:23.229 --> 01:57:26.462
<i>V redu,
pripravi se, Ryan.

01:57:29.070 --> 01:57:32.329
Počakajmo,
da preneha zvoniti.

01:57:38.479 --> 01:57:42.904
Ne snemajte še. Oprosti, Ryan,
čakamo, da preneha zvoniti.

01:57:43.587 --> 01:57:46.804
<i>Od kod prihaja to zvonjenje?

01:57:47.686 --> 01:57:52.512
<i>Še vedno čakamo.
